### v1.9.2
### RDPS NOTE: if you or anyone in your raid swaps gear presets, please wait up to 20s before pulling for the stats server to get updated gear info
### GENERAL NOTE: boss only damage is turned on by default when meter is started. this might be why you aren't seeing anything recorded in chaos dungeons.
#### BUG FIXES AND IMPROVEMENTS
- fix filtering for veskal guardian raid
- fix filtering for thaemine g3 and g4
- fix incorrect boss name for thaemine g3 swords
- added separate boss for thaemine g4 prokel
- removed giant darkness swords as bosses for thaemine g4
- removed random bosses for thaemine g4


full patch notes on [github](https://github.com/snoww/loa-logs/releases/latest)
